author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Visual International Says In Negotiations Which May Have Material Effect On Price Of Co's Securities​
text:
Jan 30 (Reuters) - Visual International Holdings Ltd :
* ENTERED INTO NEGOTIATIONS WHICH, IF SUCCESSFULLY CONCLUDED, MAY HAVE A MATERIAL EFFECT ON PRICE OF COMPANY‘S SECURITIES​
* ‍NEGOTIATIONS ARE FOR A POTENTIAL ACQUISITION BY VISUAL WHICH MAY CONSTITUTE A REVERSE TAKEOVER DEPENDING ON FINAL TERMS AGREED​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
